                <div class="card-header">
                    <h3 style="text-align: center;"><span class="text-center panel-title-text" style="font-size: 21.8px;text-align: center;">Ostvarujete popust od 20% za online plaćanje.</span><img class="img-fluid panel-title-image" src="/accepted_cards.png"></h3>
